'''William Conrad'''  was the narrator of the original 1977 television broadcast of ''[[The Making of Star Wars]]''.

His voice was replaced by that of [[Don LaFontaine]] for the 1995 VHS release of the special, which was a mail-in prize offered by the [[Wikipedia:Kellogg's|Kellogg Company]].

